snippet.title: Supermarket Mania - Match 3: Shopping Adventure Frenzy for Google Play,  August 2018
snippet.description:
Roll up your sleeves! It’s time to switch and match treats on hundreds of unique levels to open new supermarkets and expand your grocery chain. If you have ever wanted to run your own business, then seize this opportunity and see how easy and fun it could be!

Play FREE on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.g5e.smmmtch3pg.android
